    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《孤独的灵魂》是一款快节奏的砍杀类 Roguelite 游戏，融合了流畅的连击战斗与策略性技能构筑。你将扮演强大而张扬的征服者瓦鲁斯，深入混乱神塔的核心，完成注定之战。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的努力将决定是否能为瑞维莉娅点燃希望之火——她是一位正堕入黑暗的孤独灵魂。精准打击、符文升级与不断变化的挑战，使每次营救都充满新的危险与机遇。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用战斗展现自我</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗讲求风格与精度。释放致命连击，与秩序守护者缔结契约，重塑技能并提升装备稀有度。预言可赋予强力加成，但前提是你有勇气迎接更高风险的试炼。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/1f5bbf5a40118f43456da40fb66f842a.poster.avif?t=1762689284\" width=1170 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/1f5bbf5a40118f43456da40fb66f842a.webm?t=1762689284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>第一次胜利只是开始</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抵达神塔核心只是旅途的起点。踏入挑战之门，对抗强化敌人并揭示真正的结局。每一次重返都带来新威胁、战术变化，以及超越自我的机会。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/9e37099b7289e86647cd0da907dfe22e.poster.avif?t=1762689284\" width=1170 height=527 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/9e37099b7289e86647cd0da907dfe22e.webm?t=1762689284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打败敌人，构筑专属流派</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人会掉落神秘符文，你可将其镶嵌进庞大的技能树中，强化装备、解锁强大能力。策略分配资源，构建从高爆脆皮到坚不可摧的流派组合。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/8003d7eae6aa91fbad27a5ef8b6c37dd.poster.avif?t=1762689284\" width=1170 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/8003d7eae6aa91fbad27a5ef8b6c37dd.webm?t=1762689284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从守护者到征服者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是瓦鲁斯，昔日的阴影守护者。如今踏上险境，只为拯救被困神塔深处的瑞维莉娅——一位前任征服者。穿越三层迷雾重重的区域，成为她通往光明的最后希望。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/f911ef68e8b5f0e574f05212b5245afd.poster.avif?t=1762689284\" width=1170 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/f911ef68e8b5f0e574f05212b5245afd.webm?t=1762689284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>楼层守卫从不讲武德</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一层都以激烈的首领战作为终结。守卫拥有独特特性，需要玩家不断调整战术应对。注意——他们濒死时会召唤致命投影，进一步升级战斗节奏与压力。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/82f89d9af18d1ed323a36d6ca1dfe170.poster.avif?t=1762689284\" width=1170 height=526 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/82f89d9af18d1ed323a36d6ca1dfe170.webm?t=1762689284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
